name: FPropertyEntry
doc: Structure to represent a single property the user wants to bake out for a given set of materials

Property: Property which should be baked out
bUseCustomSize: Whether or not to use the value of custom size for the output texture
CustomSize: Defines the size of the output textures for the baked out material properties
bUseConstantValue: Wheter or not to use Constant Value as the final 'baked out' value for the this property
ConstantValue: Defines the value representing this property in the final proxy material
